IS_TEST().details: A flag to indicate that this is a test contract.

failed().details: Checks whether any test has failed so far. In addition to the local failure flag, we look for the global flag in the HEVM contract at storage slot "failed", because it is possible to run assertions between different instances of PRBTest.
